{"tid":2215740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]發現手足嘅去向","createTime":"2020-09-24T07:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T08:13:26.000Z","uid":306676,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3855f6030c4d97bf699b8511cf4e3eb7efe2950c","tid":2215740,"uid":306676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"《越南快報》（VNExpress）9月22日報道，越南政府負責監察市場的部門9月19日展開突擊搜查，在涉事地下工場發現32.4萬個使用過的避孕套，重達360公斤，調查人員也在現場找到數千個已包裝完整、準備出售的避孕套，未有印上商標。<br />\n<br />\n把避孕套洗淨烘乾再出售<br />\n<br />\n政府部門表示，該場地由一名32歲女子租下，她在義安省出生長大，之後到平陽省居住及工作。她無法出示文件證明這些貨品的合法來源。<br />\n<br />\n據這名女子稱，每相隔一個月左右，就會有「不知名者」帶來數千個已使用過的避孕套給她，然後她的工作就是把它們洗淨、烘乾再整理，讓它們看起來像新的一樣，當作新商品售賣給顧客。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">應承我 手足唔係condom！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7a0b4d34b428ff5d3d8d16fef9ad3d36b8b077ed","tid":2215740,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcdd3f71faac58dc846fe77f69b6016af95b80cc","tid":2215740,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"好post一定要推"},{"pid":"a21ac52be2dcc467da65e4ab2077eece2fdd3013","tid":2215740,"uid":306676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"自推10連(1/10)"},{"pid":"030e35a4a666f2103f0af4fff2274cae5fde50d2","tid":2215740,"uid":306676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"自推10連(2/10)"},{"pid":"7c2ebb2c3e6f0bbd6ce8e8e49849a151df7ff94e","tid":2215740,"uid":306676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"自推10連(3/10)"},{"pid":"8f1fa6880c6e2a7988368b67329d64b66e0d7782","tid":2215740,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"黎緊10.1 又有幾百個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr